cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.CC. 

The paper deals with updating and reasoning about knowledge bases, which are central topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The use of logic programs and update policies also suggests a connection to databases (cs.DB) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the investigation of semantical and computational properties points to a possible connection to computational complexity theory (cs.CC).
